Class ColouredDoor

  • java.lang.Object
    • Cell
      • Door
        • ColouredDoor

  • public class ColouredDoor
extends Door
    Characters will be stopped from moving onto a Coloured Door tile if it is closed and they do not have a keycard of the correct colour. The ColouredDoor class is a subclass of the abstract Door class.
    Creation Date: 20/11/19.
    Last Modification Date: 4/12/19.
    Version:
    1.3
    Author:
    Timothy Roger (977422), Nihal Goindi (976005)
